                        <interp inst="t18400302-name-646" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM GREEN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—I was a witness against him—he is the same person—he was sentenced to trans<lb></lb>portation.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was guilty of that, but that is no reason why I should be guilty of this.</p>
